debrief.itemText: Please answer the following questions about your experience. Click and drag the red scrollbar to move down. Do not leave any box blank. Type ‘no’ or ‘n/a’ if you don’t have a response.
Briefly describe what you were asked to do in this experiment? (if there is existing text in the box delete it.
debrief.response: In this experiment, I was basically given a letter and a number in which I had to label whether it was closer to A or Z for the letter and whether it was greater or less than 153 for the number. I had the choice of deciding which one I would label at the given time. Before they gave the letter/number option, a shape flashed and depending on which shape it was detemined how many points you would earn for correctly labeling these figures.

debrief.itemText: Was there any part of the experiment that you found to be confusing?
Please explain anything you found confusing. (if No, type ‘No’)
debrief.response: I just found it hard to decifier the value of each shape because it seemed to change or give a random value.
